title: Should You Sell Alphabet Inc Class A (GOOGL) Stock Friday Morning?
text:

GOOGL's short-term technical score of 93 indicates that the stock has traded more bullishly over the last month than 93% of stocks on the market. In the Internet Content & Information industry, which ranks 81 out of 146 industries, the stock ranks higher than 94% of stocks.
